                     <button class="poi" style="top: 50%; left: 50%;" data-title="Central Protostar" data-info="A large mass that forms by contraction of the gas of a giant molecular cloud. The protostellar phase is the earliest one in the process of stellar evolution."></button>
                     <button class="poi" style="top: 70%; left: 25%;" data-title="Protoplanetary Disk" data-info="A rotating circumstellar disc of dense gas and dust surrounding a young newly formed star, from which planets may eventually form."></button>
