        <section id="level-5" class="zoom-level" data-level="5" aria-labelledby="level-5-title">
            <div class="level-content">
                <h2 id="level-5-title">The Journey Continues</h2>
                <p>From the infinitely large to the infinitesimally small, the patterns repeat. The universe is a story of scale, and this is just one path. The exploration is endless. Press the <strong>Home key</strong> or the <strong>Restart button</strong> to begin again.</p>
            </div>
